# Generated daily-results markdown. It's a redundant mirror of the published
# site's results page (site/results.html, built from data/ in CI), and was the
# one file both the scheduled cloud agent and local harvest regenerated and
# committed every matchday — the sole recurring merge conflict. Untracked so
# both actors only touch data/, which auto-merges. Run generate_results.py
# locally any time to regenerate it for browsing.
/docs/results.md

